* Iron Raptor watched Plintissa get up and cling to the wall, she plunged 
her inner mouth even deeper onto Rampage.
Even though Plintissa was loose she still had a little matter to settle with 
Rampage, for when he had struck her in the head with the but of his gun!
It was then that Iron Raptor began to feel the energy loose that she knew 
would eventually happen, she snarled and thrashed her head around trying to 
rip the Predacon limb from limb.
She only had 3 clicks of power left and wanted to use it all on Rampage, 
every last drop!! She called to Plintissa with a muffled voice since she had 
an entire Predacon shoulder in her mouth...*

" Plintisha! Iff I eber let him go den get in and coffer for me, OK?!"
